%s graphics uses screen shaders for drawing weather, clouds, and particles behind translucent blocks and vodka.
this may severely impact performance for portable devices and 4k displays.

Capitalist graphics balances performance and quality for the majority of machines.

Slavic graphics reduces the amount of visible rain and snow.
transparency effects are disabled for various blocks such as leaves.
